{%- comment -%}
  Phase W — "Virtual Try On" theme app extension block (gateway).

  Merchant drops this block onto the product template (typically inside
  the main product section, above the form / Buy section). Renders a
  link styled like the theme's primary button.

  Click behaviour (Phase W):
    Opens the Vibe screen in a new tab at
    /apps/vibe/style?productId={{ product.id }}. The Vibe-app
    loader picks up the numeric id, fetches the catalog row via the
    engine's GET /v1/catalog/products/by-shopify-id/{id}, and
    renders a single-product PDP card as the first assistant turn.

    `product.id` (not `product.handle`) because catalog_enriched
    indexes by shopify_product_id (the GID) — the engine
    constructs `gid://shopify/Product/{id}` server-side and
    matches against that. Handles aren't a column on the table.

  The previous V.3 modal popup (file upload + result card in-place)
  is retired — the new tab IS the entry point to Vibe, where the
  customer's body photo is on file (or onboarded in-chat) and the
  try-on renders inline on the seeded PDP card. See Phase W in
  docs/OPEN_TASKS.md for the full flow.

  Anonymous customer identity = localStorage["vibe_session_id"]. Same
  UUID the Vibe Conversation page uses, so the body photo persists
  across surfaces; the new tab inherits it because both surfaces sit
  on the merchant's *.myshopify.com domain (same-origin localStorage).
{%- endcomment -%}

{{ 'virtual-try-on.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- liquid
  assign label = block.settings.label | default: 'Virtual Try On'
-%}

<div
  class="vibe-tryon-block"
  data-product-id="{{ product.id }}"
  data-product-handle="{{ product.handle }}"
  {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
>
  <a
    class="vibe-tryon-button"
    href="/apps/vibe/style?productId={{ product.id }}"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener"
  >
    <svg class="vibe-tryon-button-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
      <path d="M9 4l3-1 3 1 4 2v4l-2 1v9H7v-9l-2-1V6l4-2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      <path d="M12 3v5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
    </svg>
    <span>{{ label | escape }}</span>
  </a>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Virtual Try-On",
  "target": "section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "label",
      "label": "Button label",
      "default": "Virtual Try On"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
